resources.string: Little man, or little lady? It’s a surprise for us too! Come join us celebrating our newest addition to the family.
Twinkle, twinkle little star\nHow we wonder what you are
Since we’ve got a Bun in Oven, We’re firing up the grill to celebrate the baby to be with Burgers and Brats\nJoin us as we celebrate.
We shall be privileged to have you in one of the most auspicious moments of our life.
Girl or boy? Either way we will be filled with joy.
